# Mirage Unreal SDK Server
This server integrates Mirage Unreal SDK to blockchain and WalletConnect.

## Install

    npm install
    npm run start

## Endpoints

|  |  |  |
|--|--|--|
|GET|**/ping**|Check server|
|POST|**/abi**|Send ABI to server|
|GET|**/abi/:hash**|Get ABI with hash|
|POST|**/connect**|Retuns uri for connect WalletConnect bridge|
|POST|**/connection**|Check if connection session is valid|
|POST|**/get/data**|Query data from blockchain|
|POST|**/get/transaction**|Get given transaction id from blockchain|
|POST|**/get/changes**|Get events from blockchain|
|POST|**/sign/message**|Send Sing Message function|
|POST|**/verify/message**|Call Verify Message function|
|POST|**/call/method**|Call method from ABI|
|POST|**/send/transaction**|Send prepared transaction to WalletConnect|

